        <h2 class="display-5 link-body-emphasis mb-1">Breaking Down the Laptop Lifecycle: How Old Laptops Are Recycled Responsibly</h2>
        <p class="blog-post-meta">January 3, 2025 by Teng Yik Shen</p>
        <p>Millions of laptops are retired each year, but few people understand what really happens to them. In this blog, we explore how laptops are responsibly recycled—from collection and data wiping to materials recovery—and why responsible disposal is more important than ever.</p>
        <hr>

